      • addItem

        public boolean addItem(java.lang.String s,
                       int quantity)
        Parameters:
        s - the String representing the item to place on the shelf
        quantity - the number of items "s" to be placed on the shelf
        Returns:
        returns true if the quantity of item "s" has been added to the shelf and false if adding the quantity of items "s" would cause the shelf to exceed the maximum shelf capacity (note that in this case, the items are NOT added).

      • removeItem

        Returns:
